To forward a version of a package:
1 - Right-click on the version that you want to forward and select 'Forward' from the menu. Note that you must be online.
2 - In the dialog that appears, select the names of the people that you want to forward the version to.
3 - You can also type the name of a contact or an e-mail address in the text control. As you type, a menu may appear making suggestions. You can select a name from the list to save you typing the whole name.
4 - Multiple entries should be separated by commas.
5 - Press the 'Forward' button.